app deploy - Deploy the app

Deploys the application to the given target.

Usage:
  app deploy [options] [arguments] [args...]

Inherited Flags:
  -v, --verbose  Verbose output

Inherited Options:
  -c, --config  Config file

Flags:
  -f, --force  Skip confirmation
  --dry-run    Print plan without executing (default: true)

Options:
  -r, --region  Target region (default: us-east)

Arguments:
  <target>  Deploy target name
